   Now itâ€™s time to test if everything youâ€™ve done works properly:
     * Enable the â€˜Preview Modeâ€™. Click on the arrow next to the â€˜Publishâ€™
       button and select â€˜Previewâ€™.
     * Load your web page with â€˜#agencyâ€™ appended to the end of your URL,
       like this: https://yourdomain.com/#agency
     * Then, using Google Tag Managerâ€™s Preview Mode, open the â€˜Page Viewâ€™
       tag and look through the â€˜Variablesâ€™ menu.
     * You should see the â€˜Lookup â€“ URL â€“ Fragment â€“ Campaign Nameâ€™,
